            "value": "<p>You emit a cloud of toxic smoke that temporarily obscures you from sight. Each creature except you in the area when you @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Cast a Spell]{Cast the Spell} takes [[/r 1d6 #poison]] poison damage (basic Fortitude save). A creature that critically fails the saving throw also becomes @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 1}. All creatures in the area become @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Concealed]{Concealed}, and all creatures outside the smoke become Concealed to creatures within it. This smoke can be dispersed by a strong wind.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The damage increases by [[/r 1d6 #poison]].</p>"
